03:40.877 --> 03:46.823
not really a major factor in human protein supply. 
And it's probably true that we can't get more than

03:46.843 --> 03:57.255
100 million tons of fish out of the ocean by the 
present fishing techniques. We've exploited all

03:57.275 --> 04:00.418
resources intelligently.

